Name: 戦国の木こり
About the game: 'War era Lumberjack' is a mini-game in the process of making a simulation game during the Warring States period in Japan. This is a game in which you have a lumberjack cut down trees and compete for how much wood you can collect within a certain period of time. Players can only order which trees to cut.
